Description: Read, process, and analyze intracranial
    electroencephalography and deep-brain stimulation with 'RAVE', a
    reproducible framework for analysis and visualization of 'iEEG' 
    by Magnotti, Wang, and Beauchamp, (2020, <doi:10.1016/j.neuroimage.2020.117341>). 
    Supports 'BIDS' <https://bids.neuroimaging.io> or native file conventions to
    ingest signals in 'HDF5', 'Matlab', 'EDF', 'BrainVision', or 'BlackRock'
    formats; process images in 'NIfTI' and 'FreeSurfer' formats, providing
    brain imaging normalization to template brain, facilitate 'threeBrain'
    package for comprehensive electrode localization, see "your advanced
    electrode localizer" ('YAEL') by Wang, Magnotti, Zhang, and Beauchamp 
    (2023, <doi:10.1523/ENEURO.0328-23.2023>).
